title: Stranger Than Fiction: Cory Doctorow
description: Tim Wu talks with Cory Doctorow, a science fiction writer and copyright activist who is the author of such books as Little Brother and Homeland. Stranger Than Fiction is a co-production of Slate and the New America Foundation.
